---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Level 2: Technical SEO | Waseem's SEO Guide">
  <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <ol>
      <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/level1">Level 1</a></li>
      <li aria-current="page">Level 2: Technical SEO</li>
    </ol>
  </nav>

  <header>
    <span class="badge">LEVEL 2</span>
    <h1>🛠️ Technical SEO Mastery</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">From Basics to Advanced: robots.txt, Status Codes, XML Sitemaps & Core Web Vitals</p>
    <div class="reading-time-badge">⏱️ ~45 min read</div>
  </header>

  <section class="intro-section">
    <h2>What is Technical SEO?</h2>
    <p>Technical SEO is about making sure search engines can easily crawl, index, and understand your website. It's the foundation that all your other SEO efforts build upon.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>📚 Topics Covered</h2>
    <ul class="topics-list">
      <li>✓ Introduction to Technical SEO</li>
      <li>✓ The Security Guard (robots.txt)</li>
      <li>✓ The Table of Contents (XML Sitemaps)</li>
      <li>✓ The Bot's Language (Status Codes)</li>
      <li>✓ Speed & Performance Basics</li>
      <li>✓ Core Web Vitals Metrics</li>
      <li>✓ LCP, FID, CLS Explained</li>
      <li>✓ Technical Audit Checklist</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <div class="content-coming-soon">
    <p>🚧 Full content coming soon! This is a preview of the Astro-based structure.</p>
    <p>In the meantime, you can view the <a href="/level1">Level 1 content</a> for a complete example.</p>
  </div>

  <nav class="level-nav">
    <a href="/level1" class="nav-btn">← Level 1: SEO Basics</a>
    <a href="/level3" class="nav-btn">Level 3: Advanced GEO →</a>
  </nav>
</Layout>

<style>
  .breadcrumbs ol {
    display: flex;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .breadcrumbs a {
    color: #667eea;
  }

  header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .badge {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #764ba2 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 25px;
  }

  .topics-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .topics-list li {
    padding: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .content-coming-soon {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3e0 0%, #ffe0b2 100%);
    border-radius: 15px;
    margin: 40px 0;
  }

  .level-nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
  .level-nav .nav-btn {
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #764ba2 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }
</style>
